 Ali puno je bolje

1009
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:29,160
 da platimo 20 tisuća

1010
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,080
 i za sve nas,

1011
00:30:30,080 --> 00:30:32,000
 puno jeftinije 20 tisuća eura.

1012
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,020
 Jer to su ljudi

1013
00:30:33,020 --> 00:30:34,260
 koji će biti na socijalnoj pomoći.

1014
00:30:34,260 --> 00:30:35,220
 Njih 4-5 člana u obitelji.

1015
00:30:35,220 --> 00:30:38,200
 Pa tu će uskoro ide.

1016
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,680
 Pa to je gotova stvar.

1017
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:41,120
 Što to znači?

1018
00:30:41,120 --> 00:30:41,380
 Ajde, dajte podijelite s nama.

1019
00:30:41,380 --> 00:30:42,340
 To znači ovako.

1020
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:44,100
 Znači u praksi to izgleda ovako.

1021
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:46,500
 Znači Italija uvozi sa meloni

1022
00:30:46,500 --> 00:30:48,040
 i dalje će uvoziti

1023
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:50,180
 ogromne količine imigranata

1024
00:30:50,180 --> 00:30:50,940
 iz Afrike,

1025
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:54,120
 probrat će ono što im se sviđa,

1026
00:30:54,120 --> 00:30:55,700
 što im se čini upotrebljivo,

1027
00:30:55,700 --> 00:30:57,520
 neke malo bolje radnike,

1028
00:30:57,520 --> 00:30:58,660
 neke sposobnije ljude,

1029
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:00,480
 a ovo ostalo će svi nama slati.

1030
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:01,520
 Tako i Njemačka.

1031
00:31:01,520 --> 00:31:04,700
 Isto, ona sa ovih svojih milijon imigranata

1032
00:31:04,700 --> 00:31:06,040
 uzme najbolje,

1033
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:07,580
 a nama će ići i ono drugo.

1034
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:09,020
 Znači, to će biti ljudi

1035
00:31:09,020 --> 00:31:11,160
 koji će biti isključivo na socijalnoj pomoći,

1036
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,140
 zato ja kažem,

1037
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:15,560
 bolje plati 20.000 eura po glavi,

1038
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:17,280
 manje će nas koštati

1039
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:19,960
 nego da uzimamo socijalne slučajeve

1040
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:22,120
 iz Afrike i Bliskog Istoka.

1041
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:24,160
 A što ako nam prodaju priču,

1042
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:26,300
 pa evo, nema naših ljudi,

1043
00:31:26,300 --> 00:31:27,580
 nema ko bi radio,

1044
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:28,860
 pa i ovo je dobro došlo.

1045
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:31,280
 Evo, na žalost, upravo to čitamo svaki dan

1046
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:34,260
 u tim globalističkim medijima,

1047
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:37,080
 većinom u vlasništvu Srbije.

1048
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:40,520
 Čitamo da, eto,

1049
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:42,880
 oni rade poslove koje mi ne bi željeli.

1050
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:45,380
 Molim, koliko se ja sjećam,

1051
00:31:45,380 --> 00:31:47,020
 do prije koje godine,

1052
00:31:47,020 --> 00:31:49,920
 svi dostavljači hrane u Hrvatskoj

1053
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:51,760
 su bili hrvatski kađer.

1054
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:53,440
 Susjedi i tako dalje.

1055
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,880
 Gdje su nestali?

1056
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,600
 Kakve su to laži i gluposti?

1057
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,240
 Pa nisu nestali,

1058
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,620
 nego ove možeš platiti

1059
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:00,920
 nikoliko on opet sretan.

1060
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:02,680
 Njih tisuću nakrcaš,

1061
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:03,720
 ono, uše,

1062
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:04,820
 nije kreveti na kat,

1063
00:32:04,820 --> 00:32:06,860
 nego sad su kreveti nebuderi

1064
00:32:06,860 --> 00:32:07,540
 u jednoj sobi.

1065
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:09,400
 Znači, gdje spavaju kosardinice,

1066
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,360
 ono, 30 centimetara ima

1067
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:12,860
 prostor za vuce i to je to.

1068
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,280
 I ljudi rade ono jer dolaze

1069
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,680
 iz još siromašnijih država

1070
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:18,000
 i taj novac njima znači.

1071
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,660
 Ali to je put u nestanak

1072
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:20,540
 mirovinskog fonda.

1073
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:21,400
 To je put, znači,

1074
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,200
 nema mirovina.

1075
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,840
 Mi već sada nemamo

1076
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,500
 za isplatu 50% mirovina.

1077
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:27,720
 A sad zamislite još

1078
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:28,900
 sa tom količinom

1079
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,660
 ljudi koji rade za još manje.

1080
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:31,940
 Ko će onda uopće

1081
00:32:31,940 --> 00:32:33,580
 u Hrvatskoj ostati od Hrvata?

1082
00:32:33,580 --> 00:32:35,780
 Pa, zamjena stanovništva

1083
00:32:35,780 --> 00:32:37,440
 u Hrvatskoj je moguća

1084
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,860
 za doslovce 3 mjeseca.

1085
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:40,560
 Doslovce 3 mjeseca.

1086
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:43,120
 Vi imate, mi već sada imamo

1087
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:45,480
 300 tisuća stranih radnika.

1088
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,960
 Malo samo izmijenite

1089
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,380
 zakonodavstvo kao što je

1090
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:50,240
 izmijenjeno u Francuskoj.

1091
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,120
 Znači što je Macron

1092
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:53,340
 savršeno izveo prevarom

1093
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:54,340
 Marine Le Pen.

1094
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:57,860
 I, znači, imate 300 tisuća.

1095
00:32:57,860 --> 00:32:59,480
 Njima dozvolite, znači,

1096
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,180
 dovođenje obitelji,

1097
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:02,460
 sjecanje državljanstva

1098
00:33:02,460 --> 00:33:03,240
 i oni imaju pobidu

1099
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,600
 na izborima za 3 mjeseca.

1100
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:05,160
 Evo ih milijuni.

1101
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:07,240
 Znači 300, znači pročna obitelj je

1102
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:10,100
 vani pet, u Hrvatskoj je 2 ili 1.

1103
00:33:10,940 --> 00:33:11,680
 Plus pas.

1104
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,720
 Plus pas, barim 1.

1105
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:14,760
 Da, barim 1.

1106
00:33:14,760 --> 00:33:18,020
 Mislim, kod nas je dovedeno,

1107
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:20,080
 znači Hrvatska ima 60%

1108
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:21,080
 kućnih ljubimaca.

1109
00:33:21,080 --> 00:33:23,180
 Znači, kućni ljubimci su uvijek

1110
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:24,940
 bili dopuna obitelji,

1111
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:26,420
 a sada kućni ljubimci

1112
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:28,280
 postaju zamjene obitelji.

1113
00:33:28,280 --> 00:33:30,060
 Jel vas to sablažnjava?

1114
00:33:30,060 --> 00:33:30,960
 Mene da.

1115
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:32,400
 svakog normalne.

1116
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,360
 Zato što, znači,

1117
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:36,320
 lijepa je ljubav od bilo koje životinje.

1118
00:33:36,320 --> 00:33:37,580
 To je ona jednostavna ljubav.

1119
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:38,460
 Da, pa svi imamo naše male.

1120
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:39,640
 Maha ne repom i to.

1121
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:42,100
 Ali ljudsko biće ne može

1122
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:43,760
 zadovoljiti svoju potrebu

1123
00:33:43,760 --> 00:33:44,740
 za socijalnim,

1124
00:33:44,740 --> 00:33:46,700
 angažmanom i interakcijom

1125
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:48,400
 bez drugih ljudi.

1126
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,360
 To nas je i dovilo

1127
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,780
 do ovog standarda koji imamo.

1128
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:52,420
 Gospodine Kolakušiću,

1129
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:54,980
 ta naša država propada

1130
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:55,960
 na svim razinama.

1131
00:33:55,960 --> 00:33:56,700
 Sad će neko reći,

1132
00:33:56,700 --> 00:33:57,280
 joj, pa ne,

1133
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:57,780
 ti mi smo,

1134
00:33:57,780 --> 00:33:59,720
 pobjedili smo Srbiju u ratu.

1135
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,060
 Da.

1136
00:34:00,060 --> 00:34:01,260
 Da.

1137
00:34:01,260 --> 00:34:02,420
 Jesmo.

1138
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,040
 Da, jesmo.

1139
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:04,580
 Da, jesmo, ali danas je 2024.

1140
00:34:04,580 --> 00:34:04,940
 A di su novci?

1141
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:06,760
 Da, da, di su nam novci.

1142
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:08,920
 Ta Srbija bi uskoro trebala,

1143
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,600
 bi trebala u EU.

1144
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:13,460
 E, onda bi Hrvatska trebala

1145
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:15,380
 odlučivati isto tako o tome

1146
00:34:15,380 --> 00:34:18,140
 i postati na neki način

1147
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:19,700
 kao da postanemo dobri susjedi.

1148
00:34:19,700 --> 00:34:21,120
 Ali zapravo vi tu vidite

1149
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,580
 jedan priličan problem.

1150
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:25,040
 A referiram se na ukidenje jednoglasnosti.

1151
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:25,400
 Tako je.

1152
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,760
 Znači, ono jednoglasnost

1153
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,100
 koju oni govore kao

1154
00:34:28,100 --> 00:34:29,680
 Orban, Crna, Ovca,

1155
00:34:29,680 --> 00:34:31,640
 moramo sve obuke donositi.

1156
00:34:31,640 --> 00:34:33,620
 Ali evo što to na jednom primjeru

1157
00:34:33,620 --> 00:34:35,220
 odnosa Hrvatske i Srbije znači.

1158
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:36,440
 Znamo kako je išlo

1159
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,800
 kada smo mi ulazili u EU.

1160
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:40,240
 Slovenija je zahtjevala rješenje

1161
00:34:40,240 --> 00:34:42,480
 piranskog zaljeva i tako daj.

1162
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,880
 Znači, Srbija je napala

1163
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:45,780
 Republiku Hrvatsku.

1164
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,880
 Znači, vojnici Srbije su ratovali

1165
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:50,180
 na teritoriju Hrvatske države.

1166
00:34:50,180 --> 00:34:52,620
 Napravili su ogromnu štetu.

1167
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:56,100
 Ubili su skoro 20.000 ljudi.

1168
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:58,220
 Znači, mi imamo pravo

1169
00:34:58,220 --> 00:34:59,260
 na ratnu očtetu.

1170
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,700
 Kao što su imale

1171
00:35:00,700 --> 00:35:02,320
 i u drugom svjetskom ratu

1172
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:03,440
 sve države od Njemačke.

1173
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:04,680
 Tako i mi imamo pravo

1174
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:05,600
 na ratnu očtetu

1175
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:06,900
 od Srbije.

1176
00:35:06,900 --> 00:35:08,860
 Kad imate,

1177
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:11,700
 kad zadržimo princip jednoglasnosti,

1178
00:35:11,700 --> 00:35:12,620
 onda Hrvatska kaže

1179
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:14,100
 ne može dok nam ne isplate

1180
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:14,880
 ratnu očtetu.

1181
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,800
 Stavite to

1182
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,800
 u napregorački stol.

1183
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:20,800
 Kada se ukine jednoglasnost,

1184
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,820
 ne samo da mi možemo

1185
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,900
 lajat na mjesec,

1186
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,620
 nego ćemo i lajat na mjesec.

1187
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,600
 Znači, ništa od zahtjeva

1188
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:29,620
 za ratnom oštetom

1189
00:35:29,620 --> 00:35:30,560
 dok postojimo.

1190
00:35:30,560 --> 00:35:31,740
 Drugo,

1191
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:33,380
 pošto je Hrvatska

1192
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:35,260
 već 10 godina dobiva

1193
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:36,400
 iz evropskih fonda

1194
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,900
 više nego što uplačuje,

1195
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:41,120
 to razdoblje uskoro ide kraju.

1196
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:44,160
 Sada, oni koji će biti,

1197
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:45,060
 koji nam se pridružaju

1198
00:35:45,060 --> 00:35:46,600
 u EU će dobivat više.

1199
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:49,000
 Srbija, Bosna i Hercegovina, Crna Gora.

1200
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,500
 A mi ćemo Hrvati

1201
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:52,380
 i hrvatski građani dobijat manje.

1202
00:35:52,380 --> 00:35:54,300
 Znači, mi ćemo već

1203
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:55,220
 kad Srbija uđe

1204
00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:56,580
 financirati,

1205
00:35:56,580 --> 00:35:58,840
 direktno financirati

1206
00:35:58,840 --> 00:36:01,400
 razvoj, gospodarski razvoj Srbije.

1207
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,980
 I opet ništa o tome ne znamo,

1208
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:03,680
 niko o tome ništa ne govori.

1209
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:05,140
 Niko o tome ne priča

1210
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:05,940
 i tako dalje.

1211
00:36:05,940 --> 00:36:08,920
 Da, zvuči, zapravo,

1212
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,720
 zvuči vrlo, rekla bih,

1213
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:13,540
 negativistički, depresivno.

1214
00:36:13,540 --> 00:36:14,800
 To su činjenice.

1215
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,000
 A mi sad idemo građani,

1216
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:17,000
 smo tu, imamo izbori.

1217
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,160
 Ajmo, ajmo, e da,

1218
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:19,760
 što očekujete od tih izbora?

1219
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,900
 Da, izbori mogli smo imati...

1220
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:22,820
 Govorimo o EU izborima,

1221
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:25,000
 od ovih više nemamo očekivati.

1222
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,660
 Znači, EU izbori imali smo

1223
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:28,060
 opriliku, govorio sam to

1224
00:36:28,060 --> 00:36:28,980
 nekoliko puta,

1225
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,360
 da se te suverenističke

1226
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:32,900
 stranke udružile.

1227
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:34,340
 Sad vidimo domovijski pokret,

1228
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:35,420
 nema veze,

1229
00:36:35,420 --> 00:36:36,360
 to je turbo slok,

1230
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:36,600
 suverenizam,

1231
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:38,380
 nema nikakve veze.

1232
00:36:38,380 --> 00:36:38,920
 Znači,

1233
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:39,840
 prodaja za

1234
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,520
 ni kiki,

1235
00:36:40,520 --> 00:36:41,380
 ni kolače.

1236
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:43,180
 Znači, mi smo mogli imati

1237
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,780
 šest mandata

1238
00:36:44,780 --> 00:36:46,200
 u Evropskom parlamentu.

1239
00:36:46,200 --> 00:36:48,280
 Jer smo na prošljim izborima,

1240
00:36:48,280 --> 00:36:48,840
 znači,

1241
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:50,060
 građani su dali

1242
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:52,500
 370 tisuća glasova

1243
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:54,340
 na prošljim Evropskim izborima

1244
00:36:54,340 --> 00:36:55,480
 i to je bilo šest mandata.

1245
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,760
 Nažalost,

1246
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,400
 to mlijeko je

1247
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,280
 proliveno.

1248
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,280
 Sada će

1249
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,220
 HDZ

1250
00:37:00,220 --> 00:37:01,700
 ostvariti veliki rezultat.

1251
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:04,440
 Mi ćemo se boriti

1252
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,080
 na tom suverenizskom spektru

1253
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:06,520
 za

1254
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:09,000
 0, 1 i 2.

1255
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:11,040
 Ja sam uvjeren

1256
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:12,120
 da pravo i pravda

1257
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:14,140
 kao jedina prava opcija

